--Aim_Spectral

+Build Time
- 4 hours

+Spawns
- 30 Total

+Textures
-Basic colors with border. Very simple to make

+Walkway?
Covered above-ground path which leads from one side of the map to the other.
Underneath it is supported by a fairly interesting wall

+Water?
-Added in the two ditches because i didnt like how open it was on the bottom floor

+Size
-Small but fun with small groups :-)
